Class CourseNodeTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • CourseNodeTest

  • public class CourseNodeTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Test Class of the CourseNode class. This class is the main structure behind the custom course list. Tests getters and setters, usually creating a 2-3 element lists out of CourseNodes.
